<h1><b>JustChess.org</b></h1>

<div class="about-text">
	<p><b>A multiplayer chess server started in 2024 by Artem Bielikov</b></p>

	<h3>Features:</h3>
	<ul>
		<li>Match history</li>
		<li>Glicko-2 rating system</li>
		<li>Skill-based matchmaking</li>
		<li>Multiple concurrent games</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Note:</h3>
	<p>Please submit any bug reports, feature suggestions, and other feedback either to<br/>
	<a href="mailto:support@justchess.org">support@justchess.org</a> or via <a href="https://github.com/treepeck/justchess/issues">GitHub Issues</a>. Such contributions are highly appreciated.</p>

